high_descs: Turn around and then turn to your right to face the coffee table
Pick up the newspaper from off of the table
Turn around so that you are facing the sofa
Set the newspaper down on the sofa cushion
Take some steps to the left and turn right to face the small chair
Pick up another newspaper off of the chair
Head back to your right to face the sofa again
Set the second newspaper down on the sofa cushion
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the sofa

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the coffee table on the right.
Pick up the newspaper in front of the tissue box.
Turn around and face the green couch.
Put the newspaper down on the middle cushion of the green couch.
Turn left and walk to the chair to the left of the green couch.
Pick up the newspaper on the right from the green couch.
Turn right and move back to the the front of the green couch.
Place the newspaper down on the couch to the right of the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: To move two newspapers to the middle cushion of the green couch.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small coffee table and turn right when you get to it.
Pick up the newspaper that's in front of you.
Turn around to face the couch behind you.
Put the paper in the center of the center cushion near the edge closest to you.
Turn left and walk to the chair that's to the left of the couch and turn to face it when you get to it.
Pick up the paper that's farthest to the right.
Go back to where you put the first paper.
Put this paper to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two papers on the couch.
